meta {
  name: 04 - Error - Only Year Provided
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

get {
  url: {{host}}/usage/workspace-eval-summary/?workspace_id={{workspace_id}}&year=2024
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

params:query {
  workspace_id: {{workspace_id}}
  year: 2024
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

docs {
  ## Workspace Evaluation Summary - Year Without Month

  ### Test Scenario
  - workspace_id and year provided but month is missing
  - Tests validation that month and year must be provided together

  ### Expected Response
  - Status: 400 Bad Request
  - Response structure:
    ```json
    {
      "status": false,
      "message": "Error message about missing month"
    }
    ```

  ### Notes
  - Month and year must be provided together
  - Cannot provide just one of them
}
